OL,3,CBritish Sign Language videos to be
OL,4,Cscreened in cricket grounds
OL,6,FAnti-discrimination videos using
OL,7,FBritish Sign Language (BSL) will be
OL,8,Fscreened by the England and Wales
OL,9,FCricket Board at all first-class
OL,10,Fgrounds this summer.
OL,12,FJoel Harris and Jake Oakes from the
OL,13,FEngland Deaf team helped teach BSL to
OL,14,Fover 70 men's and women's players from
OL,15,Facross the country, with the results
OL,16,Fset to be shown at domestic and
OL,17,Finternational matches in the 2024
OL,18,Fseason.
