OL,4,Cscreened in cricket grounds
OL,6,FHarris, an Ashes winner in Australia
OL,7,Fin 2022, welcomed the initiative,
OL,8,Fwhich comes as part of Sign Language
OL,9,FWeek.
OL,11,F"The players have been amazing in the
OL,12,Fway they have wanted to learn," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"We're not asking the players to be
OL,16,Fknowledgeable, but they've wanted to
OL,17,Fknow more.
