OL,6,F"We've taught them their lines and
OL,7,Fsome of the basics like how important
OL,8,Ffacial expressions and body movement
OL,9,Fis alongside hand gestures. They're
OL,10,Fsmall but important things for the
OL,11,Fdeaf community to feel welcomed.
OL,13,F"It's about helping people be more
OL,14,Faware, which what we're doing here is
OL,15,Fall about. My experience is that most
OL,16,Fpeople want to be inclusive."
